# Log Completed Tickets

When completing a ticket (PR, task, or work item), always add an entry to the **Log** section of:

`docs/planning/multi-tenant-productization-prd/work-log.md`

Add a new row at the top of the Log table with:
- **Date** — Today's date (YYYY-MM-DD)
- **Ticket / Task** — PR number, ticket ID, or short task name
- **Summary** — Brief description of what was done

Example:
| Date | Ticket / Task | Summary |
|------|---------------|---------|
| 2026-03-12 | p1_pr04 | Migrated /locations to enqueue via Supabase pgmq |
